you have revealed your deepest fear

547
01:28:21.565 --> 01:28:24.944
I sentence you to be exposed

548
01:28:24.944 --> 01:28:28.030
Before your peers

549
01:28:28.030 --> 01:29:17.705
Tear down the wall

550
01:31:36.176 --> 01:31:38.637
