551
01:31:38.679 --> 01:31:41.140
Or in two's

552
01:31:42.433 --> 01:31:47.521
The ones who really love you

553
01:31:50.482 --> 01:31:53.193
Walk up and down

554
01:31:53.193 --> 01:31:55.904
Outside the wall

555
01:32:01.201 --> 01:32:06.123
Some hand in hand

556
01:32:07.082 --> 01:32:12.463
Some gathered together in bands

557
01:32:13.923 --> 01:32:20.512
The bleeding hearts
and the artists

558
01:32:20.512 --> 01:32:21.764
Make their stand

559
01:32:25.017 --> 01:32:31.774
And when they've given you their all

560
01:32:31.774 --> 01:32:34.735
Some stagger and fall

561
01:32:34.735 --> 01:32:37.696
After all. it's not easy

562
01:32:39.114 --> 01:32:41.700
Banging your heart

563
